bdbtest - Berkeley DB example
Colin King <cking@m202.net>

This application demonstrates the C++ API of Berkeley DB (bdb).
It has been tested on Ubuntu with the following packages:
libdb5.1++-dev
libreadline-dev

$ make
g++ -lreadline -ldb_cxx bdb_test.cc -o bdb_test
$ ./bdb_test 
DB file name: test.db
Command (g=get, p=put, q=quit): p
Enter key: 123
Enter value: Hello BDB!
Command (g=get, p=put, q=quit): g
Enter key: 123
Data = Hello BDB!
Command (g=get, p=put, q=quit): q

